# Cloudflare Pages security headers — media-store-ui (multi-tenant SPA).
#
# This file is served as-is by Cloudflare Pages from the build output root
# (Vite copies public/ verbatim). It is the AUTHORITATIVE source of CSP /
# HSTS / framing headers for *.earnlumens.org tenant subdomains; the meta
# tags inside index.html are only a defence-in-depth fallback for environments
# that don't honour these (file:// previews, local dev).
#
# Notes on the CSP:
#  - 'unsafe-inline' on script-src is required by the inline GTM bootstrap
#    in index.html. Tracked in SECURITY-TODO: replace with a SHA-256 hash or
#    move the gtag stub into a same-origin module so the directive can be
#    removed.
#  - 'unsafe-inline' on style-src is required by Vuetify (runtime style
#    injection). Vuetify does not support nonces yet.
#  - connect-src is intentionally same-apex-wide ('https://*.earnlumens.org')
#    so a tenant page on acme.earnlumens.org can hit api.admin… via the
#    edge router IF/when needed; today the API is same-origin so this is a
#    safety margin.
#  - frame-ancestors 'none' blocks clickjacking (X-Frame-Options is sent for
#    legacy browsers).
#  - frame-src whitelists the Stellar wallet popups we currently integrate
#    with via the Stellar Wallets Kit (Lobstr web wallet). Browser-extension
#    wallets (Freighter, xBull) talk via window.postMessage and don't need
#    a frame-src entry.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://www.googletagmanager.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https:; media-src 'self' blob: https:; font-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self' https://*.earnlumens.org https://horizon.stellar.org https://horizon-testnet.stellar.org https://www.google-analytics.com https://*.analytics.google.com https://*.googletagmanager.com; frame-src 'self' https://lobstr.co https://*.lobstr.co; worker-src 'self' blob:; manifest-src 'self'; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; upgrade-insecure-requests
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), camera=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=(), interest-cohort=()
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-site
